# video / hyperframes

Wrapper for HyperFrames — HTML/CSS/GSAP motion, no React build step.
Upstream: https://hyperframes.dev

controls do
  video.title: { label: "Composition title", type: "text" }
  video.duration: { label: "Duration (seconds)", type: "text" }
end

## Failure modes

- **Headless render** — needs Chrome/ffmpeg wired; v1 scaffolds `comp.html` only.
